{
  "stem": "27129.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You see, if the chair you did-- wasn't comfortable, you know, the chair was wobbly, you said something about the chair, you talk against the government.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And little by little, it add up, and they send you away to a camp, to a labor camp, to slave labor camps.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so you talk against the government, so you're against, uh-- against Communism.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You were not even, uh, politically inclined, you know, but you were against-- against Communism.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that's all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I knew to watch out, you know, and not to talk against the government, because it wouldn't help you if you do.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They had-- they had people that were, uh-- they were, uh-- how do you say it?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The police took them in, especially to spy on other citizens, you know, even in their own family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So if somebody asks you questions, you know, you knew-- oh, like some guys told me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Oh, I heard in Poland it was so good, you know, and it was-- life was a lot better than here.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I said, are you kidding?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "What do you mean life is better?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was a lot worse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You don't know how good you have it here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So he said, oh, I know there's-- in the-- in the stores, there's a lot of, uh, stuff, a lot of food, a lot of that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I said, because people, uh, don't have jobs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They don't make any money, so they can't buy the-- the-- the stuff, so it stays in the-- in the stores.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Nobody buys it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Nobody can afford it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Here, if you got a little money, you run to the store and the shelves are empty.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So that saved me a lot of trouble.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
